text.tspan: Introducing Visitor Badge Management — a smarter, more secure approach to visitor identification.
Powered by QR code integration, this feature eliminates manual recordkeeping and streamlines the verification process. Each visitor is issued a
digital, time-limited badge that can be easily scanned and authenticated at any checkpoint.
The result is a system that enhances efficiency, transparency, and professionalism, ensuring every visitor’s presence is both traceable and
well-managed — a reflection of your organization’s commitment to modern security standards.
